Nike Membership at JD Privacy Notice
Nike Membership at JD Privacy Notice
Company Name: JD Sports Fashion plc
      ("
JD
")
Company Number: 01888425
Territory: UK
WHO DOES THIS NOTICE APPLY TO?
This
                    privacy notice (this "
Notice
") explains how JD
                    processes your personal information in connection with the Nike Membership at JD programme (the "
the "Nike Membership at JD Programme", "Nike Member at JD ").
").
If you would like to learn about how your personal information is processed more broadly please visit:
The JD (general)
privacy notice
The Nike
privacy notice
Everything we do at JD is about you!
        We take our customers privacy and security very seriously and we are
        100% committed to protecting it so you can shop away without a single
        worry. If you have any questions about how we protect your privacy,
        just shout us @
Privacy.Support@jdplc.com
